00:11:20.680 --> 00:11:24.240
I'm thankful that our God is the God of all comfort,

00:11:24.240 --> 00:11:26.800
we read that in 2 Corinthians chapter number one,

00:11:26.800 --> 00:11:28.280
and what a blessing to know

00:11:28.280 --> 00:11:30.280
