that we'll look within this text of Scripture

00:12:11.920 --> 00:12:15.160
with regard to how God's presence brings us comfort.

00:12:15.160 --> 00:12:18.640
He tells them not to be troubled.

00:12:18.640 --> 00:12:20.920
We find that as he continues to develop the thought

00:12:20.920 --> 00:12:23.080
